they want to sell their products in the single European market.
To help product formulators label their products correctly Safeware Systems
of Kegworth has developed a PC software package which identifies the correct
risk label to put on the product - there are about 100 of them.
The package also helps formulators decide which ingredients to swap in order
to change the hazard levels. Diluting many chemicals can reduce the danger
factor, for example. The package could also reduce the need for animal
testing. Safeware Systems: UK, 0509 672656.
