recent consolidation. Dealers said the scope for further gains in the short
term would depend on the extent to which origins stepped up sales following
the price rise. COCOA closed just above the day's lows with the market still
on the defensive after Monday's weak performance. Chart sentiment has become
increasingly bearish in the last couple of days.
