FT  10 DEC 92 / Observer: Older and wiser
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
What a difference a year makes. Just 12 months ago, the theme of James
Capel's Global Investment Seminar was 'Growing into a new world order'.
Today's 1992 event is: 'Expect nothing and you won't be disappointed'.
