Oliver Prentice, formerly md/vice-president of Holiday Inn Worldwide, has
been appointed md of COMMUNITY HOSPITALS GROUP's continuing care division.
*****
Rodney Westhead, a former managing partner of Grant Thornton's London office
and recently a partner in the Northamptonshire practice, has been appointed
group finance director of RICARDO INTERNATIONAL.
